{"tid":2172334,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]韓廠日服ちびっこヒーローズ放置系RPG (4) 經驗值2倍 入坑襯早","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T17:40:07.000Z","uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"052925dba4244f25165a976b7a561aab0b793fb2","tid":2172334,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.biglobe.ne.jp/economy/0717/9297748110/d10988-543-504504-0_thum800.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.biglobe.ne.jp%2Feconomy%2F0717%2F9297748110%2Fd10988-543-504504-0_thum800.png&h=3601d11d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chibikoheroes.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chibikoheroes.com%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=a20e8bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chibikoheroes.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chibihero.pmang.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchibihero.pmang.jp%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=8df51e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://chibihero.pmang.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gamewith.jp/gamedb/games/images/2x/10b1a227dc62f1efabfcf10214094d60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gamewith.jp%2Fgamedb%2Fgames%2Fimages%2F2x%2F10b1a227dc62f1efabfcf10214094d60.jpg&h=dc5c7bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://onlinegame-pla.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4-24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinegame-pla.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F4-24.jpg&h=f6b5bc84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIOS:<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%81%A1%E3%81%B3%E3%81%A3%E3%81%93%E3%83%92%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BA-%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%B3%BBrpg/id1517992825?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2F%25E3%2581%25A1%25E3%2581%25B3%25E3%2581%25A3%25E3%2581%2593%25E3%2583%2592%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25AD%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2582%25BA-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25B3%25BBrpg%2Fid1517992825%3Fl%3Den&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=8b84c5b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%81%A1%E3%81%B3%E3%81%A3%E3%81%93%E3%83%92%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BA-%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%B3%BBrpg/id1517992825?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\nAN:<br />\nQOOAPP<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/14758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F14758&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=ed85cdb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/14758</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>Brown dust </strong></span></span>間廠出<br />\nGAME名叫<span class=\"gold\">覺醒勇士放置RPG</span><br />\n<br />\n抽裝抽同伴刷裝  放置為主<br />\n岩玩既集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">主要玩日服,左右SER都有人玩</span><br />\n[size=4]<span class=\"orange\">連登公會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n右ser :<br />\n公會1 : 光復香港 <br />\n公會2 : 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n左ser :<br />\n公會1 : 時代革命[/size=3]</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"large\">首抽</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 是但一件<span class=\"violet\">不滅武(紫色武)</span>開局<br />\n2. <span class=\"violet\">不滅+2</span>效果既裝備先開局<br />\n<span class=\"small\">(有心理準備刷幾日)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5oH3X7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5oH3X7.jpg&h=65d5cc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(因為有冇不滅+2真係差好遠,同埋刷首抽最好開模擬器刷,一次刷完3次,DEL左模擬器再開過黎刷,其實唔刷都冇所謂,因為不滅裝出唔到套裝效果既話都係廢)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">遊玩流程:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/743DKcF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F743DKcF.jpg&h=b505d9d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(神聖劵要換果3件黃色裝)<br />\n一開頭有3張神話劵+6張地獄券<br />\n<br />\n當你抽曬紅石之後<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">(千祈唔好拎紫石去抽,一定唔好,留返黎買船同開錢關)</span></strong><br />\n起碼要有上面既配置,如果你用紅石抽到上面既裝就慳返一張券<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRysCzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRysCzT.jpg&h=51c75866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當你好似我下圖咁抽完曬啦(當我冇抽到不滅裝)<br />\n睇自己差咩裝 就將最後個3張地獄券換咩<br />\n好似我咁 得劍 冇副手  咁咪換近戰副手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6m2rAn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6m2rAn.jpg&h=882b8824&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n抽曬同換曬要用既野就將有既錢拎去升武,是但升到幾多都冇所謂(我個人強化方式係武會多過頭/甲100LV,多過副手150-200LV)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YkR4nB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YkR4nB.jpg&h=760a185f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n升齊野啦,同埋將個幾件黃裝換下屬性(戒要有貫通,其他就轉增加輸出既詞),換完就上時裝,每件時裝是但比100石落去加下能力,搞掂曬就可以開始玩啦,前期推下主線,刷下錢關,升下裝(緊記只升3樣野,武&gt;頭/甲&gt;副手),升到咁上下就趁有加倍既時候打下龜,打到龜6開始有地獄裝跌,係龜6之前就用神話裝頂住冇裝既位先<br />\n<br />\n經驗方面<br />\n起手打龜獲得既經驗係唔差,但係之後會發現打主線既經驗會多過龜好多<br />\n<br />\n金幣方面<br />\n最重要既野,都係金幣副+加倍打龜+冇龜打主線<br />\n<br />\n飛船<br />\n先出尻尾船用黎掛龜結晶<br />\n<br />\n升星<br />\n根據台仔既經驗,只會食同級裝備去升星,唔會食下等裝去升<br />\n</span><br />\n台仔攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/vZRYGX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FvZRYGX&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=6c52cf19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/vZRYGX</a><br />\n巴哈<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=37455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FB.php%3Fbsn%3D37455&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=b23ffc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/B.php?bsn=37455</a><br />\n心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37455&amp;snA=221&amp;tnum=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D37455%26snA%3D221%26tnum%3D6&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d18602f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37455&amp;snA=221&amp;tnum=6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">萬巴日服0課心得</span><br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><strong>首抽唔洗點刷啦紫裝拎左都冇套效冇咩作用</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">你睇台仔都係叫你拎+2紫套之前都唔用紫套<br />\n當然你課長隨便用啦話明0課skip吧<br />\n最緊要有武有副手有甲/頭就開波<br />\n自選換隻地獄虛空戒,套裝效果+1<br />\n仲有一件睇你缺咩<br />\n神聖換皇帝套加錢<br />\n項耳腰3件<br />\n打錢關/掛機可用<br />\n頭鞋可配神聖套-cd/爆率<br />\n咁就輕鬆玩<br />\n夠你推到龜8<br />\n推唔到係你裝強化唔夠<br />\n記得只強化武盾甲/頭<br />\n不停掛機拎龜key拎錢<br />\n有石多就買副本次數前期打錢關</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/NDrWjPU.png&amp;h=ef901a2b&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n有咩唔明再問"},{"pid":"61a540bb98fab54457e4e02e1ac7e839522db1b1","tid":2172334,"uid":69546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"新手想問下地獄光係邊用?"}]}